			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I&#8217;m happy to say that Cisco has <a href='http://newsroom.cisco.com/dlls/2008/corp_110308.html'>completed its acquisition</a> of Jabber, Inc. My start date at Webb Interactive Services (original parent of Jabber, Inc.) was November 1, 1999, and my start date at Cisco was October 31, 2008. Just a day shy of 9 years! I&#8217;m looking forward to many more years of working on Jabber, XMPP, and real-time communication.</p>
